; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
; AutoUpdate.manual-targets.ini — template
;
; Copy this file to AutoUpdate.manual-targets.ini (same directory) to seed
; the Manual Targets wishlist on your local machine. The real file is
; .gitignore'd and must never be committed — it's a LOCAL-ONLY pre-handoff
; intent capture: a list of AHK scripts you want Claude to add to the
; auto-updater. Click "Copy for Claude" in AutoUpdate.ahk's Manual Targets
; panel to turn the list into a paste-ready prompt for a fresh Claude
; session. Once Claude integrates the script, this AutoUpdate auto-installs
; it at the Local Folder you specified.
;
; Prefer the built-in GUI — launch AutoUpdate.ahk and use the Manual Targets
; panel on the right side of the main window. The form's "📁 Browse" button
; picks the folder where the script should land; the GUI writes here.
;
; Each intent lives in its own [intent:Name] section:
;
;   description   what the script should do (free-form prose; multi-line
;                 supported via the ||N|| sentinel encoding)
;   localFolder   the folder on this machine where the script lands
;
; Intents are NOT polled or fetched. They exist only to drive the Copy-for-
; Claude handoff — they never enter the live TARGETS array.
; ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

; [intent:AutoMuteDiscord]
; description = Auto-mutes Discord whenever a Zoom call joins the foreground, then un-mutes when Zoom backgrounds.
; localFolder = C:\LAIS\autoHotkey

; Developed by: ShadowAISolutions
